text: Marek Avamere (born 26 January 1970) is an Estonian rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Estonian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Estonia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pärnu
